ghost...?

tell me why you're here, big sister?

Boy Bueno: I came here to become a mature man because I was
being made fun of by my older brothers!

but it's been quite difficult to get out, and also...

brothers will definitely make fun of me again!

Boy Bueno: Big sister, you're also one of the people here,
right? Then please make me into a mature man!

brothers always always make fun of me.
Boy Bueno: I don't want to be made fun of anymore...

Thief Nora: I can't make you into an adult, but... I'll do
something a little [mature-like] for you, okay?
